OL,3,CEast Midlands Airport fined nearly
OL,4,C#900,000 for polluting the Diseworth
OL,5,CBrook
OL,7,FEast Midlands Airport has been fined
OL,8,Falmost #900,000 for polluting the
OL,9,FDiseworth Brook with chemicals used to
OL,10,Fde-ice planes and runways.
OL,12,FBosses of the Castle Donington
OL,13,Ffacility admitted three separate
OL,14,Fenvironmental offences during a court
OL,15,Fhearing in April.
OL,17,FA judge at Derby Crown Court today
OL,18,F(July 28th) fined the airport #892,500
OL,19,Fand ordered it to pay #55,647.84 costs.
