OL,4,C#900,000 for polluting the Diseworth
OL,5,CBrook
OL,7,FJudge Martin Hurst said members of the
OL,8,Fpublic reported sewage fungus in both
OL,9,Fthe River Trent and Diseworth Brook in
OL,10,Fearly 2021.
OL,12,FInvestigations revealed that leaking
OL,13,Fof contaminated water had come from
OL,14,Fwhat he called "a poorly maintained"
OL,15,Fstorage pond.
OL,17,FAll the charges involved excessive
OL,18,Flevels of Biochemical Oxygen Demand
OL,19,F(BOD) in wastewater discharged from
OL,20,Fthe airport's facilities.
