OL,7,FThe Environment Agency grants EMA a
OL,8,Fpermit to discharge de-icing materials
OL,9,Finto the River Trent and nearby
OL,10,FDiseworth Brook between November and
OL,11,FApril each year.
OL,13,FHowever, the permit specifically
OL,14,Frequires that these discharges should
OL,15,Fnot have "adverse effects" on plants
OL,16,For animals in the water.
