OL,3,CEast Midlands Airport fined nearly
OL,4,C#900,000 for polluting the Diseworth
OL,5,CBrook
OL,7,FCampaigners from Fish Legal and Derby
OL,8,FRailway Angling Club had previously
OL,9,Fraised concerns about the airport's
OL,10,Foperations, claiming the facility was
OL,11,Fbreaching its permit.
OL,13,FThey reported that a fungus had been
OL,14,Fgrowing on the riverbed as a result of
OL,15,Fthe reported contamination.
OL,17,FEMA's first offence dates back to
OL,18,FJanuary 14th, 2022, when the airport
OL,19,Fexceeded permitted levels in discharge
OL,20,Ffrom the Western Summer Pond (a water
OL,21,Fstorage unit).
