OL,7,FThe managing director of the airport
OL,8,Fsaid that since the matters came to
OL,9,Flight, it has worked with the
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency and has implemented
OL,11,F#11m of improvements.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the hearing, East
OL,14,FMidlands Airport Managing Director
OL,15,FSteve Griffiths said: "I'm sorry that
OL,16,Fin 2022 there were issues with the
OL,17,Foperation of our water drainage
OL,18,Fsystem, which led to breaches of our
OL,19,Fpermit on three occasions.
